      "queue_index": 14,
      "source_index": 14,
      "post_uri": "at://did:plc:otadxbi4rzrmydgsq5a4tg42/app.bsky.feed.post/3mkarkfc22y2j",
      "cid": "bafyreieqqzcbpbkp53djmx6caxnzgnnsnjn3sgav5ixflkgqkb4hyxdj4u",
      "posted_at": "2026-04-24T14:49:53.710542+00:00",
      "text_hash": "3b981a82883d37b166a5e7d1ba3525fddf7ad3854dcac7394f15f47eb2607a65",
      "post_text": "Today's name is Kala-kanthaya. The dark-throated one, bearing the poison of the cosmic ocean. Jai Bhairava Baba. #Kalabhairava"
    },
    {
      "queue_index": 15,
      "source_index": 15,
      "post_uri": "at://did:plc:otadxbi4rzrmydgsq5a4tg42/app.bsky.feed.post/3mkaumtoz7y2v",
      "cid": "bafyreidpwxrlagedywxfpogtcom6mt3jsdqttu7vu6zuwwsnpqmks4hb24",
      "posted_at": "2026-04-24T15:44:57.119192+00:00",
      "text_hash": "84c8d77ba2b4b8c048b47b4e4fb0fd30ece64a4a7308a490872536318aead486",
      "post_text": "Today's name is Kataksa-anugrahita-akhila-sevakaya. Whose gracious glance blesses all his devotees. Jai Bhairava Baba. #Kalabhairava"
    },
    {
      "queue_index": 16,
      "source_index": 16,
      "post_uri": "at://did:plc:otadxbi4rzrmydgsq5a4tg42/app.bsky.feed.post/3mkaw4y65ng2v",
      "cid": "bafyreid6irhwjegosl3nm67jnv4ot4eqwtbl4qnnjzwkrhjclwndrrnrqe",
      "posted_at": "2026-04-24T16:11:52.431411+00:00",
      "text_hash": "ed5cdf7ca14583d3a5c0da4e2a63b15152c47e94bd315b910c57efbac0b97f27",
      "post_text": "Today's name is Kapala-karparotkrista-bhiksa-patra-dharaya. Holder of the uplifted skull-bowl, symbolizing renunciation and sacred detachment. Jai Bhairava Baba. #Kalabhairava"
    },
    {
      "queue_index": 17,
      "source_index": 17,
      "post_uri": "at://did:plc:otadxbi4rzrmydgsq5a4tg42/app.bsky.feed.post/3mkaxktqqlx2o",
      "cid": "bafyreid4xbtcdnmyucpaxregjt6ucwnkbx653gfiedatkjjwhcbphiqjza",
      "posted_at": "2026-04-24T16:37:31.314801+00:00",
      "text_hash": "a05f24c909f09794f03d0754c17a7c2676b52c75528734cd6d73c71b48eccb6a",
      "post_text": "Today's name is Kavaye. The supreme poet and knower of all wisdom. Jai Bhairava Baba. #Kalabhairava"
    },
    {
      "queue_index": 18,
      "source_index": 18,
      "post_uri": "at://did:plc:otadxbi4rzrmydgsq5a4tg42/app.bsky.feed.post/3mkazfn7znr2c",
      "cid": "bafyreifrkgff2gje7brirq5a3mr236raskddtzhapogfjf5zynnq5yq7yi",
      "posted_at": "2026-04-24T17:10:24.188522+00:00",
      "text_hash": "c761824ee53c06c5f6e4d147712e6bd06a0f75364457a8d938c5b81f004cb8e3",
      "post_text": "Today's name is Kalpanta-dahanakaya. Whose form is the cosmic fire at the end of an age. Jai Bhairava Baba. #Kalabhairava"
    },
    {
      "queue_index": 19,
      "source_index": 19,
      "post_uri": "at://did:plc:otadxbi4rzrmydgsq5a4tg42/app.bsky.feed.post/3mkb2uwgq472g",
      "cid": "bafyreianndf7blxizcb6bf55nvg34zh4zg2qkwfozr3qpf7nqcvwl7m42e",
      "posted_at": "2026-04-24T17:36:50.889388+00:00",
      "text_hash": "436dc06e092c15bc6a427c5e8081bbdfe151cd92f75170e6f6e25425c587566b",
      "post_text": "Today's name is Kala-nidhi-kala-dharaya. Adorned with the moon, repository of arts and knowledge. Jai Bhairava Baba. #Kalabhairava"
    },
    {
      "queue_index": 20,
      "source_index": 20,
      "post_uri": "at://did:plc:otadxbi4rzrmydgsq5a4tg42/app.bsky.feed.post/3mkb4dy3kbs2g",
      "cid": "bafyreidpgm2osscuecwcnklrg3ocywqiwdtkyirx32pnnfqn4m7ieyc76e",
      "posted_at": "2026-04-24T18:03:09.687686+00:00",
      "text_hash": "89f1b93df2fb0292539846f734c7e5a7e27ba857961e81cc170409ea4a6c7ccf",
      "post_text": "Today's name is Kapala-malika-bhusaya. Adorned with a garland of skulls, signifying victory over ego and mortality. Jai Bhairava Baba. #Kalabhairava"
    },
    {
      "queue_index": 21,
      "source_index": 21,
      "post_uri": "at://did:plc:otadxbi4rzrmydgsq5a4tg42/app.bsky.feed.post/3mkb5ymrpbt2c",
      "cid": "bafyreic76mypjpyvrdtbqyrgj7olbqz45ng6aqyuv5qgddpv6pgygj5mre",
      "posted_at": "2026-04-24T18:32:36.201249+00:00",
      "text_hash": "6aac6e13244683456f165d320dde37bbd4eaf684fcb3bc4ed013da096a0a2290",
      "post_text": "Today's name is Kali-kula-vara-pradaya. Bestower of boons to the lineage of Kala, the stream of destinies. Jai Bhairava Baba. #Kalabhairava"
    },
    {
      "queue_index": 22,
      "source_index": 22,
      "post_uri": "at://did:plc:otadxbi4rzrmydgsq5a4tg42/app.bsky.feed.post/3mkba2yvmdx2x",
      "cid": "bafyreiemoskyu3b5kzui4sekbxn2kmhyxoimi3xk4cefmragakm2ltopwu",
      "posted_at": "2026-04-24T19:09:43.525155+00:00",
      "text_hash": "f414ffe1dce74bf2047053f793a4b53a8fc13d0494bfdc26a14549418aaa4eae",
      "post_text": "Today's name is Kalii-kalavatii-diiksa-samskara-upasana-priyaya. Delighting in initiation, purification, and worship for those who seek the mysteries of Kali. Jai Bhairava Baba. #Kalabhairava"
    },
    {
      "queue_index": 23,
      "source_index": 23,
      "post_uri": "at://did:plc:otadxbi4rzrmydgsq5a4tg42/app.bsky.feed.post/3mkbbnpidas27",
      "cid": "bafyreidgsdedezfycji6djiyk2hbsu7wsssevfc67letduoo7c4ldlvbsu",
      "posted_at": "2026-04-24T19:38:04.945702+00:00",
      "text_hash": "c00d21f90896e0820e3ccf72fee4e84b08def8ce292029f172c94f5deda0536a",
      "post_text": "Today's name is Kalika-daksa-parsva-sthaya. Seated at the right side of Goddess Kali, embodying fierce protection. Jai Bhairava Baba. #Kalabhairava"
    },
    {
      "queue_index": 24,
      "source_index": 24,
      "post_uri": "at://did:plc:otadxbi4rzrmydgsq5a4tg42/app.bsky.feed.post/3mkbd37df3y2j",
      "cid": "bafyreidfoelyowlpxjib6oh3r7hjyvodbkqojq2hgjtq4p5efr74bs7tci",
      "posted_at": "2026-04-24T20:03:31.472817+00:00",
      "text_hash": "021cc8b0eb14afb635e5eb715a6787efb36d90b7169b062cf4327d8f18402c9d",
      "post_text": "Today's name is Kali-vidya-svarupa-vate. Embodiment of the knowledge needed in the Kali age. Jai Bhairava Baba. #Kalabhairava"
    },
    {
      "queue_index": 25,
      "source_index": 25,
      "post_uri": "at://did:plc:otadxbi4rzrmydgsq5a4tg42/app.bsky.feed.post/3mkbeoc3ult2n",
      "cid": "bafyreiflt6ungcbewrm5jlxv4gou5ngevftbpkwvmb5yjfdxyx7q2nchfm",
      "posted_at": "2026-04-24T20:32:05.661057+00:00",
      "text_hash": "9a498c2683d1def732864d83f3a58d13ef905ab8d1713e7b3992cefb8e653d9c",
      "post_text": "Today's name is Kalii-kurca-sama-yukta-bhuvana-kuta-bhasuraya. Resplendent amid the seed powers that hold the universe together. Jai Bhairava Baba. #Kalabhairava"
    },
    {
      "queue_index": 26,
      "source_index": 26,
      "post_uri": "at://did:plc:otadxbi4rzrmydgsq5a4tg42/app.bsky.feed.post/3mkbglccdsc2a",
      "cid": "bafyreidfqpz2jqjskid36ylmsfe6gus3frjh3dnlm7bj4yrc35akyscnue",
      "posted_at": "2026-04-24T21:06:12.689621+00:00",
      "text_hash": "53bde0325ee10d49d115d093b2ac569653e61fa806ea6daa288442f6c5da516b",
      "post_text": "Today's name is Kalii-dhyana-japa-asakta-hrda-akarana-vasakaya. Whose heart is absorbed in meditation and mantra-japa of Kali. Jai Bhairava Baba. #Kalabhairava"
    },
    {
      "queue_index": 27,
      "source_index": 27,
      "post_uri": "at://did:plc:otadxbi4rzrmydgsq5a4tg42/app.bsky.feed.post/3mkbi5urzfc2y",
      "cid": "bafyreietvonighnbtzdupdcth2d3aachufmm2i7c4ujlmrntq63u4uxo3m",
      "posted_at": "2026-04-24T21:34:29.813635+00:00",
      "text_hash": "e2fe5481b4b815cd500de5c665e3a3d05243a6061eff223ea0bdad6e55c85e69",
      "post_text": "Today's name is Kalika-varivastyaadi-pradhana-kalpa-padapaya. The primordial wish-fulfilling tree rooted in the essence of Kali. Jai Bhairava Baba. #Kalabhairava"
    },
    {
      "queue_index": 28,
      "source_index": 28,
      "post_uri": "at://did:plc:otadxbi4rzrmydgsq5a4tg42/app.bsky.feed.post/3mkbjts2yux2q",
      "cid": "bafyreib7dyjhwfop72gsvjmyzxfiocjatpr6gzlghxmsjx6zqzjz6rxjeu",
      "posted_at": "2026-04-24T22:04:38.913467+00:00",
      "text_hash": "9874a6707f1011deadcc3949f7eb55ff1088990c16c5851576bfbeb3b7076371",
      "post_text": "Today's name is Kali-ugra-vasava-brahmii-pramukha-carya-nayakaya. Leader among the divine powers who preside in the Kali Yuga. Jai Bhairava Baba. #Kalabhairava"
    },
    {
      "queue_index": 29,
      "source_index": 29,
      "post_uri": "at://did:plc:otadxbi4rzrmydgsq5a4tg42/app.bsky.feed.post/3mkblc7prng2c",
      "cid": "bafyreiaemofc7rzp5gadixk2jy6mtowur4jdgjtsbvqzrrtuedfug7ibvu",
      "posted_at": "2026-04-24T22:30:36.702286+00:00",
      "text_hash": "693709435c19e47c595ff7b9c647f378b327e885b122bc6ac212e175601a8a7b",
      "post_text": "Today's name is Kankala-malika-dharine. Wearer of a garland of bones and skulls, victor over death. Jai Bhairava Baba. #Kalabhairava"
    },
    {
      "queue_index": 30,
      "source_index": 30,
      "post_uri": "at://did:plc:otadxbi4rzrmydgsq5a4tg42/app.bsky.feed.post/3mkbn2myi6u2s",
      "cid": "bafyreieqrthysgrsh7abuqxpx75pnjdqhrmetsjabh35irzny46j5y7nle",
      "posted_at": "2026-04-24T23:02:09.664043+00:00",
      "text_hash": "32becf858d717ef741febe2c91851123f95640e8013a5321cf1feb246b9e846c",
      "post_text": "Today's name is Kaamaniya-jata-dharaya. Beautifully adorned with matted locks. Jai Bhairava Baba. #Kalabhairava"
    }
  ]
}
